Author:
Vol / Page:  5
Edition:
Quote:  Mr Charles Bryan, a trolleyman employed at Messrs Waller and England's sawmill at Aratika met with a very severe accident on Saturday by a chain, which is attached at one end to the brake handle and the other end to the twitch chain, coming undone and catching in the packing of the gramway causing the handle to fly back with tremendous force and hit the unfortunate man on the head.
